Class Mass

java.lang.Object
  jgame.JGObject
      jboxGlue.PhysicalObject
          jboxGlue.PhysicalObjectCircle
              object.Mass

public class Mass
extends PhysicalObjectCircle

Mass object that moves in response to applied forces. Shows up as a blue circle on screen by default. When this object hits another object, the collision will be elastic. The color of the mass can be changed to differentiate among models.

Author:
Yuhua Mai, Susan Zhang
